title: R I O T, where are the missions!?
body:
https://i.gyazo.com/c1b41457697f1922d9e447b8fe4ec10b.png

250 points off, this is the second week in a row with no missions.

Stop this. I am not going to get the damn last icon now.

replies.body:
There's no more missions until the next Beta Pass in Patch 9.16. We have to wait for the other servers to catch up to OCE, since our missions were released first. I think the whole Pass goes down tomorrow so you might not be able to get it at all bud :(

https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/special-event/teamfight-tactics-beta-pass-update

Also did we actually miss a week of missions prior to this? I received missions last week. (Although I finished them in 2 days so it almost feels like I didn't). If you didn't receive any at all last week then that could be worth reporting
